FIG. 2 is an isometric view of the tire inspection and preparation device showing a wheel assembly contacting a tire;


FIG. 3 is a cross-sectional view of the tire inspection and preparation device;


FIG. 4 is an isometric view of the tire inspection and preparation device showing a dial indicator contacting the tire;


FIG. 5 is an isometric view of an alternative embodiment of the tire inspection and preparation device showing a motor assembly attached to a mount of the tire inspection and preparation device and a cutting tool contacting the tire;


FIG. 6 is a cross-sectional view of the tire inspection and preparation device of FIG. 5;


FIG. 7 is a partial isometric view of an alternative embodiment of the tire inspection and preparation device of FIG. 5 showing a motor attached to a scuffing tool;


FIG. 8 is a partial cross-sectional view of a pivot bushing;


FIG. 9 is a partially exploded isometric view of an alternative embodiment of a mounting system;


FIG. 10 is a cross-sectional view of the mounting system of FIG. 9; and


FIG. 11 is an isometric view of the mounting system in a pivoted position.
